title: Trump has 'nothing to hide' from Mueller -Moscow
text:
Trump has 'nothing to hide' from Mueller -Moscow Thursday, January 25, 2018 - 01:27 
Russia's deputy foreign minister, Arkady Dvorkovich, tells Reuters' Axel Threlfall that he's ''not surprised about anything'' in Moscow's deteriorating relationship with Washington, what he calls a casualty of U.S. domestic politics.
